title: Underestimated | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Underestimated | Joel Osteen
description:
Don’t be discouraged when people underestimate you. God is going to defy the odds so that everyone sees His favor on your life.

 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
